articles.title: F1 Monaco GP: Verstappen beats Alonso to pole by 0.084s; Perez last - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Max Verstappen snatched pole position in a breathless Formula 1 qualifying session for the Monaco Grand Prix, crushing Fernando Alonso's hopes at the death of the session.
articles.content: The Dutchman overcame a two-tenth deficit to Alonso in the final sector to make a last-gasp swoop for the fastest time, his resulting 1m11.365s cementing his first pole position in qualifying at the … [+6461 chars]
